        <div class="msgSubject">R26 Build</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-16 00:09:56 | Edited: Nov 16 2010 11:45am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1289887796187116028" id="quote-1289887796187116028" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1289887796187116028" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=186&amp;mid=1289887796187116028&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1289887796187116028&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1289887796187116028" onclick="followToggle('add','1289887796187116028')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
